casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Robert J. KERNS.
No. D-2899.
Supreme Court of the United States
May 16, 2016.
Robert J. Kerns, of North Wales, Pennsylvania, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
